  "format": "tiptap/v1",
  "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T17:46:43.949Z",
  "doc": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Image prompting supplies "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "visual input",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " — screenshots, diagrams, photos — alongside text instructions. Vision-capable models extract text (OCR), identify objects, interpret UI layout, and reason about spatial relationships for agent tasks like document review, QA testing, and visual search."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What it is"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The prompt pairs an image (URL or base64 per API) with text specifying what to extract, compare, or decide. Agents use images as evidence: error dialogs, whiteboard photos, chart screenshots."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Why it matters"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Many agent workflows are inherently visual — verifying deployed UI, reading scanned forms, inspecting maps. Text-only prompts cannot access pixels; multimodal prompts bridge that gap without a separate OCR pipeline (though OCR-specialized tools may still be more accurate for dense documents)."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "How to implement"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "attrs": {
          "start": 1
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "State task, image role (\"screenshot of checkout page\"), and output format"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Crop or highlight regions when APIs support annotations or when sending multiple detail crops"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Ask for citations to image regions (\"top-right button label\") when accuracy matters"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "codeBlock",
        "attrs": {
          "language": "text"
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Image: [checkout_error.png]\nTask: Identify the error message shown and the button the user should click next.\nOutput: {\"error_text\": \"...\", \"recommended_action\": \"...\"}"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Trade-offs"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Large images cost tokens and latency"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Small text in screenshots may be misread — verify critical OCR"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Key takeaways"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Pair images with explicit task and output schema"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Use for UI, diagrams, and visual evidence in agent loops"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Validate critical text extraction independently when stakes are high"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
